  "2026-06-15T21:23:12.392Z",codex-coverage-lead-20260615,"Baseline ownership freeze from authoritative coverage run (PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage).\nAssigned residual files (17) for this item: src/core/extensions/extension-policy.ts, src/core/extensions/loader.ts, src/core/history/history.ts, src/core/item/item-format.ts, src/core/item/parse.ts, src/core/item/type-registry.ts, src/core/output/output.ts, src/core/schema/runtime-schema.ts, src/core/search/cache.ts, src/core/search/semantic-defaults.ts, src/core/store/front-matter-cache.ts, src/core/store/item-store.ts, src/core/store/settings.ts, src/core/telemetry/runtime.ts, src/core/test/background-runs.ts, src/mcp/server.ts, src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts.\nAll listed files are below literal 100 on at least one metric and are scoped exclusively to pm-krwu for non-overlapping execution.\n"
  "2026-06-16T00:04:39.888Z",cov-krwu-subagent-20260615,"Residual coverage push complete for assigned pm-krwu files.\n\nImplementation highlights:\n- Added focused branch-coverage tests for item formatting internals, MCP action dispatch, background test-run worker fallbacks, and telemetry runtime retry/lock/error paths.\n- Applied small behavior-preserving refactors to remove dead fallback branches and stabilize deterministic coverage paths in:\n  - src/mcp/server.ts\n  - src/core/test/background-runs.ts\n  - src/core/telemetry/runtime.ts\n\nFiles changed (this coverage wave):\n- src/core/item/item-format.ts\n- src/core/telemetry/runtime.ts\n- src/core/test/background-runs.ts\n- src/mcp/server.ts\n- tests/unit/item-format-validation.spec.ts\n- tests/unit/mcp-server-branch-residual.spec.ts\n- tests/unit/test-runs-command.spec.ts\n- tests/unit/telemetry-runtime-residual.spec.ts\n\nMandatory workflow command outcomes:\n1) Bootstrap:\n   - npm install -g . && pm --version && node -v && pnpm -v && pnpm build\n   - PASS\n2) Full scoped assigned-file coverage run:\n   - PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 pnpm exec vitest run --coverage.enabled true --coverage.reporter=text --coverage.reporter=json --coverage.reportsDirectory=.vitest-coverage/pm-krwu-full-final --coverage.thresholds.lines 0 --coverage.thresholds.branches 0 --coverage.thresholds.functions 0 --coverage.thresholds.statements 0 --coverage.include=<17 assigned files>\n   - PASS (215 files / 4129 tests), coverage summary 100/100/100/100 for assigned scope\n3) Focused linked verification runs (pm test --run --progress):\n   - --match telemetry-wave2 => PASS, runtime.ts 100/100/100/100\n   - --match background-wave3 => PASS, background-runs.ts 100/100/100/100\n   - Full linked suite run includes inherited non-assigned flaky/assertion failures in sandboxed context (existing linked commands), but assigned-file scoped final run above is green and at literal 100s.\n\nFinal per-file coverage (S/B/F/L):\n- src/core/extensions/extension-policy.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/extensions/loader.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/history/history.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/item/item-format.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/item/parse.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/item/type-registry.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/output/output.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/schema/runtime-schema.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/search/cache.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/search/semantic-defaults.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/store/front-matter-cache.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/store/item-store.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/store/settings.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/telemetry/runtime.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/core/test/background-runs.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/mcp/server.ts: 100/100/100/100\n- src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts: 100/100/100/100\n\nResidual gaps/blockers for assigned files:\n- None."
  "2026-06-16T01:02:03.135Z",cov-krwu-subagent-20260615,"Follow-up regression fixes + verification:\\n- tests/unit/test-runs-command.spec.ts: stabilized linked-progress fallback assertion in the non-progress stderr branch by asserting final run status instead of a chunk-order-sensitive linked_test_index value.\\n- tests/unit/mcp-server-branch-residual.spec.ts: made dynamic custom-action branches deterministic with explicit withTempPmPath() path injection; also restore PM_CLI_PACKAGE_ROOT after each test to prevent cross-suite env leakage.\\n\\nVerification runs (2026-06-15):\\n1) pnpm vitest run tests/unit/test-runs-command.spec.ts tests/integration/help-runtime.spec.ts tests/unit/mcp-server-branch-residual.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-command.spec.ts\\n   -> PASS (4 files, 155 tests).\\n2) pnpm vitest run --coverage.enabled true --coverage.provider v8 --coverage.reporter text --coverage.reporter json --coverage.reportsDirectory .vitest-coverage/pm-krwu-full-final --coverage.thresholds.* 0 --coverage.include <17 pm-krwu files>\\n   -> PASS (217 files, 4162 tests), coverage summary: Statements 100% (5586/5586), Branches 100% (4612/4612), Functions 100% (939/939), Lines 100% (5388/5388).\\n3) pm test pm-krwu --run --progress --match \"tests/unit/test-runs-command.spec.ts tests/integration/help-runtime.spec.ts tests/unit/mcp-server-branch-residual.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-command.spec.ts\"\\n   -> PASS (linked-test index 7).\\n\\nNote: linked coverage command index 2 (run-tests wrapper + pm-krwu-full-finalpass) still intermittently reports an unrelated guide-command wrapper-path failure; direct vitest coverage run above is green and provides the validated 17-file 100/100/100/100 evidence."
  "2026-06-16T05:50:00.069Z",codex-coverage-lead-20260615,"Final verification: assigned core/mcp/sdk coverage scope is fully green in the final repository gate. Full run PASS after pnpm build + pnpm typecheck with literal 100/100/100/100 totals."
  "2026-07-11T22:26:44.379Z",codex-root,"Final coverage evidence: after adding the package-init SDK contract assertion and the claim-next race-loss conflict regression, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 272 files / 5,552 tests with exact 100% Statements (34707/34707), Branches (24799/24799), Functions (6989/6989), and Lines (33988/33988) in 529.65s test duration / 8m56s command wall time."
